#. Tag: title
#: locate.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Locate &GUI; Frontend"
msgstr "Lociraj &GUI; Frontend"

#. Tag: primary
#: locate.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Locate"
msgstr "Lociraj"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:12
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&krusader; has a &GUI; front end for the <command>locate</command> "
#| "command (findutils). Locate is used for fast file searching not from a "
#| "directory but a database. The package contains among other files, "
#| "<command>locate</command> and <command>updatedb</command>. "
#| "<command>updatedb</command> goes through the local file system and stores "
#| "the file entries in the database. <command>cron</command> often calls "
#| "<command>updatedb</command> every night (set with <application>KCron</"
#| "application>). Choose <menuchoice> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
#| "<guimenuitem>Locate</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or <keycombo action="
#| "\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> to start this "
#| "feature. <link linkend=\"konfig-advanced\">Konfigurator</link> can set "
#| "additional arguments for <command>updatedb</command>."
msgid ""
"&krusader; has a &GUI; front end for the <command>locate</command> command "
"(findutils). Locate is used for fast file searching not from a folder but a "
"database. The package contains among other files, <command>locate</command> "
"and <command>updatedb</command>. <command>updatedb</command> goes through "
"the local file system and stores the file entries in the database. "
"<command>cron</command> often calls <command>updatedb</command> every night "
"(set with <application>KCron</application>). Choose <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Locate...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> to "
"start this feature. <link linkend=\"konfig-advanced\">Konfigurator</link> "
"can set additional arguments for <command>updatedb</command>."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; ima &GUI; front end za <command>lociraj</command> komandu "
"(findutils). Lociraj se koristi za brzo pretrazivanje fajlova koji nisu u  "
"imaniku, ali su u bazi podataka. Ovaj paket sadrži pored drugih fajlova, "
"<command>lociraj</command> i <command>updatedb</command>. <command>updatedb</"
"command> ide kroz lokalni sistemski fajl i pohranjuje unošene fajlove u bazu "
"podataka. <command>cron</command> često poziva <command>updatedb</command> "
"svake noći (postavi sa <application>KCron</application>). Izaberi "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Alati</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lociraj</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> ili <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>L</keycap></"
"keycombo> da pokrenete ovu značajku. <link linkend=\"konfig-advanced"
"\">Konfigurator</link> može postaviti dodatne argumente za "
"<command>updatedb</command>."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checkbox Options"
msgstr "Checkbox Opcije"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show only the existing files</guilabel>: if the database contains "
"entries which no longer exist any more (deleted, moved since the last "
"<command>updatedb</command>), <command>locate</command> does not list them. "
"It checks the existence of each file before the listing in the results "
"window (slow)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prikaži samo postojeće fajlove</guilabel>: ako baza podataka sadži "
"unose koji više ne postoje (izbrisane,premještene od zadnje "
"<command>updatedb</command>), <command>lociraj</command> ih ne stavlja na "
"listu. Ona provjerava postojanje svakog fajla prije prikazivanja spiska u "
"prozoru za rezultate (show)."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Case Sensitive</guilabel>: unchecking it allows lower and upper "
"case search."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Case Sensitive</guilabel>: njeno poništavanje omogućava gornji i "
"donji slučaj pretrage."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Action buttons"
msgstr "Tipke za radnju"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Locate</guibutton>: executes <command>locate <replaceable>foo "
"foo</replaceable></command> and places its output into the results window."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Lociraj</guibutton>: izvrši <command>lociraj <replaceable>foo "
"foo</replaceable></command> i postavlja svoj proizvod u prozor za rezultate."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Stop</guibutton>: stops the locating process."
msgstr "<guibutton>Obustavi</guibutton>: zaustavlja proces lociranja."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>UpdateDB</guibutton>: starts <command>updatedb</command> for "
"updating the locate database after entering the root password."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>UpdateDB</guibutton>: pokreće <command>updatedb</command> za "
"ažuriranje baze podataka poslije unošenja root passworda."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Close</guibutton>: closes the locate window."
msgstr "<guibutton>Zatvori</guibutton>: zatvara prozor za lociranje."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Results window"
msgstr "Prozor za rezultate"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:79
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Double-click on an item: steps to its directory, makes the item visible "
#| "and closes the locate dialog."
msgid ""
"Double-click on an item: steps to its folder, makes the item visible and "
"closes the locate dialog."
msgstr ""
"Dupli-klik na predmet: otvara imenik, omogućava predmet vidljivim i zatvara "
"dijalog za lociranje."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Right click: edits/views/finds the menu."
msgstr "Desni klik: uredi/pregledaj/nađi meni."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F3</keycap>: views the current item."
msgstr "<keycap>F3</keycap>: pregledava trenutni predmet."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F4</keycap>: edits the current item."
msgstr "<keycap>F4</keycap>: uređuje trenutni predmet."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>: finds files "
"in the results window."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>: pronalazi "
"fajlove u prozoru za rezultate."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>: shows the "
"next search result."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>: prikazuje "
"sljedeći rezultat pretrage."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>: shows the "
"previous search result."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>: prikazuje "
"prethodni rezultat pretrage."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The results window supports dragging items to other windows and copy to "
"clipboard (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Prozor za rezultate podržava povlačenje stavkih iz drugih prozora i kopira "
"ih u međuspremnik (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></"
"keycombo>)."
